		   <span class="sm">Posted @ Sat, Nov 3rd 10:27 AM 2001 </span><span id="notbold">| <span class=sm>IP: Logged</span> | <a class=sm href="/db/classes.html?class=1&mid=100480125754049&post=1&replyto=100480125754049"><img src=/shared/reply_to_thread_ico.gif border=0 alt="Reply..." height=11 width=17> Reply to this</a></a>   <a name=100480125754049></a></small></td></tr>
		   <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href="/db/poster.html?user=103857"><span id=>FenVen</span></a><b><span id=></span></b><br>41 posts
		   <br><nobr><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Excellent [4.93]</nobr><br><br><img src="/shared/transp.gif" width="135" border="0" height="1"></td><td valign="top" class="mform" width="100%"><p>Here is the Warrior epic layed out in step-by-step...hope this helps...The 2 swords are Blade of Strategy and Blade of Tactics<br><br>Quest Start<br>Talk to Kargek Redblade and Wenden in East Freeport to start the quest.<br>Jeweled Dragon Head Hilt<br><br>1, Go to Lake Rathetear. Swim to the Flame Tower Island, then swim underwater and find the tunnel going underneath the island. <br>Pick up the Unjeweled Dragon Head Hilt. <br>2, Obtain a Diamond, Black Sapphire and Jacinth. <br>3, Give the Unjeweled Dragon Head Hilt, Diamond, Black Sapphire and Jacinth to Wenden to get the Jeweled Dragon Head Hilt. <br>Finely Crafted Dragon Head Hilt<br><br>1, Go to Timorous Deep. Go to the Chessboard Island. <br>2, Pick up the Damaged Dragon Head Hilt that is at the Chessboard. <br>3, Go to Plane of Fear. Kill Fright, Dread or Terror to get the Ball of Everliving Golem. <br>4, Go to Dreadlands. Kill all the giants at the castle until the Mountain Giant Patriarch spawns. <br>5, Kill the Mountain Giant Patriarch to get the Giant Monocle. <br>6, Go to Frontier Mountains. Give the Giant Monocle to Mentrax Mountainbone in the giant fort to get the Rejesium Ore. <br>7, Go to East Freeport. Give the Damaged Dragon Head Hilt, Ball of Everliving Golem and Rejesium Ore to Wenden to get the Finely Crafted Dragon Head Hilt. <br>Ancient Sword Blade [First]<br><br>1, Go to Ocean of Tears. Talk to Denken Strongpick and he tells you the items he wants. <br>2, Go to almost any merchant selling alcoholic beverages to buy a Keg of Vox Tail Ale. <br>3, Go to Permafrost. Kill the Ice Giants to get a Block of Perma Frost. <br>4, Obtain two Rebreathers from any player Tinkerer. <br>5, Go to Ocean of Tears. Give the Keg of Vox Tail Ale, Block of Perma Frost and two Rebreathers to Denken Strongpick to get the Ancient Sword Blade. <br>Ancient Sword Blade [Second]<br><br>1, Go to Chardok. Kill the queen to get the Ancient Sword Blade. <br>The Red Scabbard<br><br>1, Go to East Freeport. Talk to Kargak Redblade. Say "I will do you a favor" to get the letter. <br>2, Go to The Ferrott. Give the letter to Oknoggin to get the Tiny Lute. <br>3, Go to East Freeport. Give the Tiny Lute to Kargak Redblade to get the book. <br>4, Go to Highpass Hold. Give the book to Tenal Redblade to get the Frozen War Totem. <br>5, Go to Permafrost. Kill the Goblin Wizards to get the Frozen Goblin Heart. <br>6, Go to Highpass Hold. Give the Frozen War Totem and Frozen Goblin Heart to Tenal Redblade to get the Totem of Fiery War. <br>7, Go to Emerald Jungle. Kill Severlious to get the Green Dragon Scale. <br>8, Kill either Nagafin [SolB,] Ragefire [SolB,] or Talendor [Skyfire] to get the Red Dragon Scale. <br>9, Go to Highpass Hold. Give the Totem of Fiery War, Green Dragon Scale and Red Dragon Scale to Tenal Redblade to get the Mark of the Sword. <br>10, Go to Plane of Hate. Kill Hand of maestro to get The hand of the maestro. <br>11, Go to Highpass Hold. Give the Mark of the Sword and Maestro's hand to Tenal Redblade to get another note. <br>12, Go to Plane of Sky. Kill the Spiroc Lord to get the Spiroc Wingblade. <br>13, Go to East Freeport. Give the note and Spiroc Wingblade to Kargek Redblade to get the Red Scabbard, along with instuctions on how to combine the swords.<br><br><br>It is quite long,,,but its VERY worth the effort,,,many things on this list you need to be 50+ to do...to enter ANY planes you must be 46+, but most guilds dont let people go until 47 incase they die and cant get corpse back....i would join a powerful guild before doing the hard parts of your quest. And of course, go by steps,,,dont skip around =) Good luck to you<br><br><br>Fenily Venily<br>47th Barbarian Warrior<br><br>&lt;get the hell outa my way&gt;<br></p></td></td></tr><tr><td colspan="2" class="mform"><table border=0 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0 width="100%"><tr><td id=fs8></td><td align=right id=fs8 >0 Replies</td></tr></table></td></tr></table><tr><td class=mhback align=right><span class=mh id=fs8><a class=mh href=/db/classes.html?class=1><img src=/shared/root_thread_ico.gif border=0 alt="Up" width=17 height=11> Thread Index</a> |  <a class=mh href=/db/classes.html?class=1&post=1><img src=/shared/new_thread_ico.gif border=0 alt="New" width=17 height=11> New Subject</a> | <a class=mh href=/db/classes.html?class=1&mid=100480125754049&post=1&mid=100480125754049><img src=/shared/reply_to_thread_ico.gif border=0 alt="Reply" width=17 height=11> Reply to Thread</a></span></td></tr><tr><td><table width=100% border=0 cellpadding=0 cellspacing=0 class=mform><tr><td colspan=1  style='font-size: 9.5px;'>0 Posts [ <a href="/fsearch.html?base=class1">Search Forums</a> ]</nobr></td></tr></table>&nbsp;</td></tr>
